snippet.title: Turn-based Combat: Wukong vs. Spider Queen
snippet.description: Defeat your opponents by strategically playing cards (which cost energy), using consumables, leveraging relics. You will also be recruiting a team of your own, and face a team of NPCs (in PvE) or a team of human controlled players (PvP) as your opponents.
